         <abstract id="aspace_567858dd4cf849423f40876f9400c0a0">Correspondence, diaries, notebooks, clippings, printed matter and a draft history of the Richmond Armory which he headed from 1861 to 1862. Included also are notes on machinery and a British patent for small fire-arms.</abstract>
